The paper deals with generalization error bounds for learning non-convex objectives using noisy gradient methods, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
